        "content": "{\n  \"resolution_strategies\": [\n    {\n      \"resolution_strategy_id\": \"RS1_remove_self_influence_on_evaluation_extra\",\n      \"change_operations\": [\n        {\n          \"operation\": \"remove_write\",\n          \"parameters\": {\n            \"target_activity_label\": \"conduct due diligence study\",\n            \"removed_variable_name\": \"evaluation_extra\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"evaluation\": {\n        \"compliance_degree\": {\n          \"value\": \"full\",\n          \"reason\": \"The violation is caused because 'conduct due diligence study' writes 'evaluation_extra', which influences the loop condition 'data.evaluation_extra' although the activity is not prior to the condition check. Removing this write eliminates the self-influencing condition source. If 'data.evaluation_extra' is true before the loop condition is evaluated, the loop still leads to 'conduct due diligence study'.\"\n        },\n        \"resolution_context_consistency\": {\n          \"value\": \"high\",\n          \"reason\": \"The strategy does not affect 'obtain respondent bank annual report' or 'analyze respondent bank annual report' required by R1, and it does not alter the risk branch where 'data.risk' directly leads to 'terminate' required by R3.\"\n        },\n        \"change_cost\": {\n          \"value\": \"very_low\",\n          \"reason\": \"Only one localized data-write modification is required.\"\n        },\n        \"structural_quality_impact\": {\n          \"value\": \"none\",\n          \"reason\": \"The control-flow structure is unchanged. Only the data produced by one activity is adjusted.\"\n        },\n        \"change_location\": {\n          \"value\": \"middle\",\n          \"reason\": \"The change is located in the due-diligence part of the process, after request intake and risk assessment but before account-opening and reporting activities.\"\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"resolution_strategy_id\"